  "texts": [
    "Then, to investigate the differences between groups, we performed post-hoc Wilcox pairwise comparison foot_9.",
    "We found that users in group G N A N R spent significantly less time revising than users in G A R (p <.05) and G A N R (p <.05).",
    "However, we did not find any significant difference between the groups with and without reflecting prompts, thus rejecting H3-1.",
    "Next, we examined how the time spent varied between the three recipes users wrote.",
    "Figure 6 (left) illustrates the revision times of all five conditions for their first, second and third recipe."
  ]
